snippet.title: Domiverse - How to play - Uzal
snippet.description:
How to play Uzal

Last living on his submerged planet after defeating one by one all the inhabitants, this starfish is the best karateka of the universe.
Uzal uses his bubble to reach ennemies from a short range. He’s able to duck and counter with his legendary shoryuzal!

http://domiverse.be

Steam store: 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/598880/Domiverse/
